    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes. There\u2019s a little bit of character from normal use, but it still looks great and drives even better! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
