    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior traction coming out of apexes. Critical mechanical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with refreshed bushings for sharp turn-in and communicative steering feedback. A mechanically honest example optimized for performance longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Regular maintenance. Clean title.",
