      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The M96 powerplant benefits from diligent preventative maintenance, ensuring the Variocam Plus system operates flawlessly across the rev range. Chassis dynamics remain sharp with a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and communicative hydraulic steering. This driver-focused example offers a mechanical purity and analog feedback rarely found in modern grand tourers, presenting in an honest, enthusiast-maintained state.",
